# Keeps the build context small and prevents anything not needed at
# runtime from ever reaching the Docker daemon. The Dockerfile also COPYs
# explicit paths rather than the whole repo, so this is mostly a
# belt-and-suspenders / build-speed measure.
.git
.gitignore
.github/
raw_data/
data/hpo.db
scripts/__pycache__/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
node_modules/
.DS_Store
